      • idGen

        static final AtomicInteger idGen
        *All* Query parameter identifiers MUST have the following format: - If a query can be executed on multiple values of the parameter ( for example, process instance id), => Then the constant name should end with "_LIST". - If a query can only contain one value of the parameter (for example, language for task queries), => Then the constant name should only be the parameter name.
